      <title>内塔尼亚胡因战争、政治、预算而受到巨大压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/netanyahu-boxed-in-by-fierce-pressure-over-war-politics-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当以色列最高法院周一晚间否决总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的司法改革法时，他的利库德集团批评法官在对哈马斯的战争期间做出的裁决，而此时民族团结至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/netanyahu-boxed-in-by-fierce-pressure-over-war-politics-budget</guid>
